data.description: Single story home located in a growing low traffic area. Less than a mile away from RAFB. Conveniently located near a 51-acer plot of land that will consist of Sante 51 a new sub division under construction that will include Sheriff Office Substation, retail shops, car dealerships, office spaces, restaurants, and eventually a full functional hospital. 25min from Ft Sam Houston, 25min from Downtown SA, 10min from The Forum. Ideal starter home for a new family. Amenities include upgraded appliances, high ceilings, and huge master closet, and ceiling fans in every room. Wonderful home and neighborhood.  Show times 9am-2pm and 5pm-8pm.
